[package]
name = "android-wakelock"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "Stephen M. Coakley <me@stephencoakley.com>",]
edition = "2021"
description = "Safe and ergonomic Rust bindings to the Android WakeLock API"
repository = "https://github.com/sagebind/android-wakelock"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "android",]
categories = [ "api-bindings",]
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
jni = "0.21"
log = "0.4"
ndk-context = "0.1"

[[example]]
name = "get_image"
required-features = [ "image-data",]

[[example]]
name = "set_image"
required-features = [ "image-data",]

[package]
name = "arboard"
version = "3.4.0"
authors = [ "Artur Kovacs <kovacs.artur.barnabas@gmail.com>", "Avi Weinstock <aweinstock314@gmail.com>", "Arboard contributors",]
description = "Image and text handling for the OS clipboard."
repository = "https://github.com/1Password/arboard"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "clipboard", "image",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.67.1"

[features]
default = [ "image-data",]
image-data = [ "core-graphics", "image", "windows-sys",]
wayland-data-control = [ "wl-clipboard-rs",]

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.9.0"

[dependencies]
resvg = "0.42.0"
log = "0.4"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
clipboard-win = "5.3.1"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies]
parking_lot = "0.12"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48.0"
optional = true
features = [ "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Graphics_Gdi", "Win32_System_DataExchange", "Win32_System_Memory", "Win32_System_Ole",]

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "png",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2]
version = "0.5.1"
features = [ "relax-void-encoding",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-foundation]
version = "0.2.0"
features = [ "NSArray", "NSString", "NSEnumerator", "NSGeometry",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.objc2-app-kit]
version = "0.2.0"
features = [ "NSPasteboard", "NSPasteboardItem", "NSImage",]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.core-graphics]
version = "0.23"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "tiff",]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies.x11rb]
version = "0.13"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies.wl-clipboard-rs]
version = "0.9"
optional = true

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies.image]
version = "0.25"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "png",]

[package]
name = "clipboard-master"
version = "4.0.0-beta.6"
authors = [ "Douman <douman@gmx.se>",]
keywords = [ "Windows", "winapi", "clipboard",]
description = "Simple utility crate to monitor clipboard changes"
homepage = "https://github.com/DoumanAsh/clipboard-master"
repository = "https://github.com/DoumanAsh/clipboard-master"
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2018"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
windows-win = "3"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies]
x11-clipboard = "0.9"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
objc = "0.2"
objc_id = "0.1"
objc-foundation = "0.1"

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies.x11rb]
version = "0.13"
features = [ "xfixes",]

[target."cfg(all(unix, not(any(target_os=\"macos\", target_os=\"ios\", target_os=\"android\", target_os=\"emscripten\"))))".dependencies.wl-clipboard-rs]
version = "0.9"

[[example]]
name = "simple"

[package]
name = "confy"
version = "0.4.0-2"
authors = [ "Katharina Fey <kookie@spacekookie.de>",]
description = "Boilerplate-free configuration management"
license = "MIT/X11 OR Apache-2.0"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/confy"
repository = "https://github.com/rust-cli/confy"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
directories-next = "^2.0"
serde = "1.0"

[features]

yaml_conf = [ "serde_yaml",]

[dev-dependencies]

tempfile = "3.5"

[dependencies.serde_yaml]
version = "0.9"
optional = true

[dependencies.toml]
version = "0.5"
optional = true

[package]

[features]

[dependencies.uuid]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]

[package]
name = "core-foundation-sys"

[dependencies.objc2-encode]

[package]

repository = "https://github.com/servo/core-foundation-rs"

authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[features]
default = []
elcapitan = []
highsierra = []

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"

[dependencies.core-foundation]
path = "../core-foundation"

[dependencies.core-graphics-types]
path = "../core-graphics-types"
version = "0.1"

[dependencies.objc2-encode]
version = "=2.0.0-pre.2"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]

[package]
name = "core-graphics-types"
description = "Bindings for some fundamental Core Graphics types"
homepage = "https://github.com/servo/core-foundation-rs"
repository = "https://github.com/servo/core-foundation-rs"
version = "0.1.2"
authors = [ "The Servo Project Developers",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.0"
libc = "0.2"

[dependencies.core-foundation]
path = "../core-foundation"
version = "0.9"

[dependencies.objc2-encode]
version = "=2.0.0-pre.2"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
default-target = "x86_64-apple-darwin"

[[example]]
name = "evtest_tokio"
required-features = [ "tokio",]

[package]
name = "evdev"
version = "0.11.5"
authors = [ "Corey Richardson <corey@octayn.net>",]
description = "evdev interface for Linux"
license = "Apache-2.0 OR MIT"
repository = "https://github.com/cmr/evdev"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/evdev"

[features]
tokio = [ "tokio_1", "futures-core",]

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2.121"

[dev-dependencies]
itertools = "0.10"

[dependencies.tokio_1]

version = "1.17"
features = [ "net",]
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-core]
version = "0.3"

[dev-dependencies.tokio_1]
package = "tokio"
version = "1.17"
features = [ "macros", "rt-multi-thread",]

[package]
name = "hwcodec"
version = "0.4.18"
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
vram = []

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
serde_derive = "1.0"
serde = "1.0"

[build-dependencies]

bindgen = "0.59"

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.10"
rand = "0.8"

[target."cfg(target_os=\"windows\")".dev-dependencies.capture]

[target."cfg(target_os=\"windows\")".dev-dependencies.render]
path = "dev/render"

[target."cfg(target_os=\"windows\")".dev-dependencies.tool]
path = "dev/tool"

[package]
name = "keepawake"
version = "0.4.3"
authors = [ "Segev Finer <segev208@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.63"
description = "Keep your computer awake"
repository = "https://github.com/segevfiner/keepawake-rs/"
license = "MIT"
keywords = [ "caffeinate", "systemd-inhibit", "idle", "sleep", "power-management",]
categories = [ "command-line-utilities",]
exclude = [ "/tools/",]

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0"
cfg-if = "1.0"

[build-dependencies]
shadow-rs = "0.21.0"
winres = "0.1.12"

[profile.release]
strip = true
lto = "thin"

[dependencies.clap]
version = "4.3"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[dependencies.clap_complete]
version = "4.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.ctrlc]
version = "3.4"
features = [ "termination",]
optional = true

[dependencies.shadow-rs]
version = "0.21"
optional = true

[dependencies.sysinfo]
version = "0.29"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies]
zbus = "3.12"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
core-foundation = "0.9"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.48"
features = [ "Win32_System_Power",]

[package]
name = "magnum-opus"
version = "0.4.0"
authors = [ "Tad Hardesty <tad@platymuus.com>", "Sergey Duck <sergeypechnikov326@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
description = "Safe Rust bindings for libopus"
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "opus", "codec", "voice", "sound", "audio",]
categories = [ "api-bindings", "encoding", "compression", "multimedia::audio", "multimedia::encoding",]
repository = "https://github.com/DuckerMan/magnum-opus"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/magnum-opus"

[features]
linux-pkg-config = [ "dep:pkg-config",]

[build-dependencies]
target_build_utils = "0.3"
bindgen = "0.59"

[build-dependencies.pkg-config]
version = "0.3.27"
optional = true

[[bin]]
name = "mouce"
path = "src/bin/main.rs"
required-features = [ "cli",]

[package]
name = "mouce"
version = "0.2.1"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Emre Bicer <oebicer@gmail.com>",]
license = "MIT"
description = "A library that aims to help simulating and listening mouse actions across different platforms."
homepage = "https://github.com/emrebicer/mouce"
repository = "https://github.com/emrebicer/mouce"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "mouse", "events", "listen", "simulate", "click",]
categories = [ "accessibility", "command-line-utilities",]

[features]
cli = [ "clap",]

[lib]
name = "mouce"
path = "src/lib.rs"

[profile.release]
opt-level = 0

[dependencies.clap]
version = "3.1.8"
features = [ "derive",]
optional = true

[target."cfg(any(target_os = \"linux\", target_os = \"dragonfly\", target_os = \"freebsd\", target_os = \"netbsd\", target_os = \"openbsd\"))".dependencies]
glob = "0.3.0"

[package]
name = "pam"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Florian Wilkens <gh@1wilkens.org>",]
description = "Safe Rust wrappers for PAM authentication"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
categories = [ "authentication",]
repository = "https://github.com/1wilkens/pam/"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/pam/"
readme = "README.md"
include = [ "LICENSE-*", "README.md", "CHANGELOG.md", "/src", "/examples",]
edition = "2018"

[features]
default = [ "client",]
functions = []
client = [ "users",]
module = []

[dependencies]
pam-macros = "=0.0.3"
libc = "^0.2"

[dev-dependencies]
rpassword = "5.0"

[workspace]
members = [ ".", "macros",]

[badges.azure-devops]
project = "1wilkens/ci"
pipeline = "pam"

[dependencies.pam-sys]
git = "https://github.com/fufesou/pam-sys"
branch = "fix/v1.0.0-alpha4_gnuc_va_list"

[dependencies.users]
version = "^0.10"
optional = true

[package]
name = "pam-sys"
version = "1.0.0-alpha4"
authors = [ "Florian Wilkens <gh@1wilkens.org>",]
description = "FFI wrappers for the Linux Pluggable Authentication Modules (PAM)"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
categories = [ "authentication", "api-bindings", "external-ffi-bindings", "os::unix-apis",]
repository = "https://github.com/1wilkens/pam-sys.git"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/pam-sys/"
readme = "README.md"
include = [ "LICENSE-*", "README.md", "CHANGELOG.md", "src/lib.rs", "build.rs", "wrapper.h",]
edition = "2018"
build = "build.rs"
links = "pam"

[dependencies]
libc = "^0.2.65"

[build-dependencies]
bindgen = "0.59"

[badges.azure-devops]
project = "1wilkens/ci"
pipeline = "pam-sys"

[package]
name = "parity-tokio-ipc"

license = "MIT/Apache-2.0"

[[example]]

[package]

edition = "2018"
name = "rdev"

[dependencies]

lazy_static = "1.4"

widestring = "1.0.2"

[features]

[dev-dependencies]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies.core-graphics]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.epoll]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.inotify]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies.x11]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.winapi]

[package]
name = "reqwest"
version = "0.11.23"
description = "higher level HTTP client library"
keywords = [ "http", "request", "client",]
categories = [ "web-programming::http-client", "wasm",]
repository = "https://github.com/seanmonstar/reqwest"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/reqwest"
authors = [ "Sean McArthur <sean@seanmonstar.com>",]
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.63.0"
autotests = true

[features]
default = [ "default-tls",]
default-tls = [ "hyper-tls", "native-tls-crate", "__tls", "tokio-native-tls",]
native-tls = [ "default-tls",]
native-tls-alpn = [ "native-tls", "native-tls-crate/alpn",]
native-tls-vendored = [ "native-tls", "native-tls-crate/vendored",]
rustls-tls = [ "rustls-tls-webpki-roots",]
rustls-tls-manual-roots = [ "__rustls",]
rustls-tls-webpki-roots = [ "webpki-roots", "__rustls",]
rustls-tls-native-roots = [ "rustls-native-certs", "__rustls",]
blocking = [ "futures-util/io", "tokio/rt-multi-thread", "tokio/sync",]
cookies = [ "cookie_crate", "cookie_store",]
gzip = [ "async-compression", "async-compression/gzip", "tokio-util",]
brotli = [ "async-compression", "async-compression/brotli", "tokio-util",]
deflate = [ "async-compression", "async-compression/zlib", "tokio-util",]
json = [ "serde_json",]
multipart = [ "mime_guess",]
trust-dns = [ "trust-dns-resolver",]
stream = [ "tokio/fs", "tokio-util", "wasm-streams",]
socks = [ "tokio-socks",]
http3 = [ "rustls-tls-manual-roots", "h3", "h3-quinn", "quinn", "futures-channel",]
__tls = []
__rustls = [ "hyper-rustls", "tokio-rustls", "rustls", "__tls", "rustls-pemfile",]
__internal_proxy_sys_no_cache = []

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.21"
http = "0.2"
url = "2.2"
bytes = "1.0"
serde = "1.0"
serde_urlencoded = "0.7.1"
tower-service = "0.3"
sync_wrapper = "0.1.2"

[dependencies.futures-core]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.futures-util]
version = "0.3.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.mime_guess]
version = "2.0"
default-features = false
optional = true

[package.metadata.playground]
features = [ "blocking", "cookies", "json", "multipart",]

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dependencies]
encoding_rs = "0.8"
http-body = "0.4.0"
h2 = "0.3.14"
once_cell = "1"
log = "0.4"
mime = "0.3.16"
percent-encoding = "2.1"
pin-project-lite = "0.2.0"
ipnet = "2.3"

[target."cfg(not(target_arch = \"wasm32\"))".dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.10"
libflate = "1.0"
doc-comment = "0.3"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
winreg = "0.50.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
system-configuration = "0.5.1"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
js-sys = "0.3.45"
serde_json = "1.0"
wasm-bindgen = "0.2.68"
wasm-bindgen-futures = "0.4.18"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
